The following Wiki Markup:
{noformat}
# Try this
## and see
# what happens
{noformat}

Yields this text:
{noformat}
   1.  Try this
         1. and see
   2. what happens 
{noformat}

Oddly, the problem only seems to apply to the Classic Theme, Left-nav theme, and clickr theme. The Default Theme (this is Confluence 2.6 default theme) renders properly:
{noformat}
   1.  Try this
         a. and see
   2. what happens 
{noformat}

